description: This is the condo you've been waiting for! Well maintained 2 bed, 2 full bath condo featuring a spacious open concept kitchen and living room with a lovely fireplace and glass doors providing abundant natural light. The private covered porch is perfect for entertaining. The large main bedroom features dual closets and a bath with a double vanity and jacuzzi tub. A spacious second bedroom, 2nd full bath, central air, beautiful hardwood floors, and in unit washer dryer make this an ideal home. There is abundant dedicated storage in the basement. This condo is located one block from East Broadway in the heart of South Boston. Walk everywhere! Open House Saturday (12/7) 12:00 - 1:00 and Sunday (12/8) 1:00 - 2:00
